  <num>8-103.13</num>
  <heading>Mayor authorized to regulate construction.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>The Mayor may regulate construction that bears upon the quality of the waters of the District.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>No person shall construct a treatment facility which has not been approved by the Mayor before construction begins.</text>
  </para>
